Reduce the high-dimensional Sei embeddings to principal components for efficient processing.

1. Dimensionality Reduction (PCA)
Script: 2_pca.py
Input: CTCF_118_600bp-hg38_predictions.h5
Bash
python pca1.py --input /path/to/CTCF_118_600bp-hg38_predictions.h5 --output pca_result.npy

2. Graph Construction (KNN)
Construct the K-Nearest Neighbor graph based on the PCA results.
Script: 3_knn.py
Bash
python knearst2.py --input pca_result.npy --k 30

3. Clustering (Louvain)
Perform Louvain community detection to identify distinct CTCF functional clusters.
Script: 4_louvain.py
Bash
python louvainteststep3.py --input knn_graph.npz --resolution 1.0

4. Visualization (UMAP)
Visualize the clustering results using Uniform Manifold Approximation and Projection (UMAP).
Script: 5_umap.py
Bash
python umapstep4.py --input clustering_result.h5ad --output umap_plot.pdf
